      • getCasAvailableToEndEntity

        public Map<Integer,​List<Integer>> getCasAvailableToEndEntity​(int endentityprofileid,
                                                                   String endentityAccessRule)
        Method that calculates the available CAs to an end entity. Used in add/edit end entity pages. It calculates a set of available CAs as an intersection of: - The administrator's authorized CAs, the end entity profile's available CAs and the certificate profile's available CAs.
        Parameters:
        endentityprofileid - the EE profile of the end entity
        endentityAccessRule - Rule
        Returns:
        a HashMap of CertificateProfileIds mapped to Lists if CA IDs. It returns a set of available CAs per end entity profile.
